Before we ever open a single brush, we *talk*. We want to understand your vision — the aesthetic of your wedding, the vibe you're going for, your skincare history, any concerns you have, and how you normally wear your makeup day-to-day.

Are you a minimalist bride dreaming of glass skin and a subtle rose lip? A glamour queen who wants full sultry eyes and a bold moment? Somewhere in between? We listen first.

