On your wedding day, our artists arrive early, prepared, and professional. We bring a fully stocked kit, work efficiently without sacrificing precision, and create a calm, luxurious atmosphere so your getting-ready experience feels as special as the rest of the day.

We also coordinate seamlessly with your hairstylist, photographer, and wedding planner to make sure the morning timeline flows beautifully.

### 4. The Touch-Up Kit
Every Velora Bella bride receives a custom touch-up kit with the exact products used on her skin — so you can refresh throughout the day with zero guesswork.

